Example Dataset: data_verheul_2024

Source: R/data_verheul_2024.R
data_verheul_2024.Rd

An example dataset from Verheul et al., 2024, released under https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Usage

data_verheul_2024

Format

A data frame with 422685 rows and 7 variables:

value

Numeric value

variable

Character variable

trial

Character trial

participant

Character participant

data_type

Character data_type

leg

Character leg

stance

Numeric variable

Source

https://github.com/JasperVerheul/horizontal-deceleration-forces

References

Verheul J, Harper D, Robinson MA. Forces experienced at different levels of the musculoskeletal system during horizontal decelerations. J Sports Sci. 2024 Dec;42(23):2242-2253. doi: 10.1080/02640414.2024.2428086.
